column1: Double-peaked [O III] AGNs without Companions within 3"

Notes. Observing log and properties of the 75 dpAGNs without close companions in HST or Keck/LGSAO images. Column 1: J2000 designation. Type-1s are indicated by stars. Column 2: redshift. Column 3: velocity splitting between [O III] lambda5007 components. Column 4: Kellermann et al. (1989) radio loudness, $R = F_{\nu,\rm 5\, GHz}/F_{\nu,\rm 4400A}$. Column 5: name of the imager and filter. Column 6: total exposure time of the image. Column 7: UT date (yymmdd) of the image. Column 8: outside seeing at 5000 Aring during the imaging observation. Column 9: IFS data available? 1 - yes, 0 - no. Column 10: source references - (1) Liu et al. 2010b; (2) Wang et al. 2009; and (3) Smith et al. 2010.
